  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Cute",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>If you can get passed the alien nature inherent to all demons, this demon is actually pretty cute and fluffy. Three consecutive successful Resolve saves will immunize the rolling character to its Fear effects. It may still give the character the willies on occasion, but it’ll be tolerable enough to be around. The character may even have the desire to pet it.</p>",
        "action": "passive"
