    },
    {
      "name": "It's Fast",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon is very fast. Don’t bother rolling initiative for it. Give it its own initiative slot at the top of the order, and another slot in the middle of the order. These slots are individualized and not part of any group. Additionally, the demon can use Maneuvers to attack, as well as Minor Actions.</p>",
        "action": "passive"
      },
